# MISC::ABSF

## Summary
Checks the absolute value for an float, any negtaives will be returned as positive

## Parameters
* **FLOAT** n

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
See http:en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Absolute_value
